{"id":283740,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/维权网-两会将结束，浙江安吉维权人士沈志华被/","date":"2013-03-13T05:00:37Z","modified":"2013-03-13T05:00:37Z","title":"维权网 | 两会将结束，浙江安吉维权人士沈志华被强制旅游（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员裘思思报道）今年全国人大和政协两会开始时，浙江省安吉县的上访维权人士沈志华因被政府雇佣的黑帮打伤，在杭州浙二医院治疗。沈志华出院后，起诉县政府和县公安局的状子递上去了，当局对她的看管又严起来了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>因怕她再次到北京上访，梅溪镇政府综治副主任李有成、黄兆才亲自陪她自驾游。昨天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>）他们又“陪同”沈志华外出旅游：上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>时从安吉县递铺镇出发，途经安徽宁国、绩溪，下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分到黄山。因天下大雨，无法上山游玩，今天被困在黄山脚下。这次“旅游”的终点是井冈山，准备两会结束后返回。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>其实，沈志华根本没有心思游玩，她的父母亲整天提心吊胆，担心女儿会被这些把她视为眼中钉的官员害死。不过，镇党委副书记叶鸣岗保证沈志华无事，他说他会把沈志华的事“打包处理”，但一时解决不了，先出去轻松轻松。其实，想轻松轻松的怕是这些官员。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>去年十八大前，政府官员带叶根来到新疆阿克苏“轻松”，花掉公款五万多元。这次两会已开了一半他们还把沈志华带出去旅游，除了怕沈志华上北京影响他们的“政绩”外，趁此机会逍遥快活一番也是应有之义。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/--Dju3LnCT_Y/UT_3O9pEMTI/AAAAAAAAevk/EqvT41hmYW4/s1600/FILE0022_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/--Dju3LnCT_Y/UT_3O9pEMTI/AAAAAAAAevk/EqvT41hmYW4/s320/FILE0022_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vXVo9PPQ5qI/UT_3PtVeLHI/AAAAAAAAevs/PcV4U8lQS60/s1600/FILE0048_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vXVo9PPQ5qI/UT_3PtVeLHI/AAAAAAAAevs/PcV4U8lQS60/s320/FILE0048_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-bnJIYX-DAcI/UT_3QbjgyLI/AAAAAAAAev0/kyXEfyX80tw/s1600/%E5%A4%8D%E4%BB%B6+FILE0058_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-bnJIYX-DAcI/UT_3QbjgyLI/AAAAAAAAev0/kyXEfyX80tw/s320/%E5%A4%8D%E4%BB%B6+FILE0058_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}